description: The TTEP115 windshield and dashboard car mount is ideal for use with the TomTom START 40, 45, 55, and XL; XL and XXL; and ONE 125, ONE 130, and ONE 140 models. The adapter plate included with the holder accommodates any of the above TomTom models. It includes Arkon’s Travelmount deluxe mini suction car mount, an adapter plate that converts the mount from a Dual-T to the circular TomTom EasyPort mount pattern, and a 3M adhesive dashboard mounting disk.  The arm of the suction mount adjusts vertically and provides 360° rotation, giving you the ultimate flexibility in viewing the TomTom device from any angle.
title: Windshield Dashboard Car Mount for TomTom GPS with EasyPort Pattern START 40 45 55 XL XXL ONE 125 ONE 130 ONE 140 XL
